---
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
import tylerImage from '../images/tyler-sitting.jpg';
import tylerPodcast from '../images/tyler-podcast.jpg';
---

<div class="tyler-block pb-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex">
        <!-- <Image src={tylerImage} alt="Tyler Sitting"/> -->
        <div class="about-tyler relative">
            <Image src={tylerPodcast} class="tyler-pod" alt="Tyler in front of microphone for podcast" />
            <div class="tyler-content pt-8">
                <h3 class="pb-4">Hi. I'm Tyler</h3>
                <p class="text-xl">I was having a story play out in my mind of a young boy trying to pull back a bow and shoot it. He constantly waits for a man to come in and help teach him to work his bow.</p>
                <p class="text-xl">When the boy looks at his reflection in shallow waters he sees a familiar yet foreign face. There is experience and wisdom in the features around his eyes.</p>
